{{Infobox television | show_name = The Shock | image = | image_alt = | caption = | genre = [[Reality television]] | developer = | writer = | director = | starring = {{Plainlist| * [[Alaa Hussein (actress)|Alaa Huusein]] * Karim Kojak }} | opentheme = | endtheme = | composer = | country = {{Plainlist| * Egypt * Iraq * Jordan * Lebanon * Saudi Arabia * Syria * Tunisia * United Arab Emirates }} | language = [[Arabic]] | num_seasons = 2 | num_episodes = 60 | list_episodes = | executive_producer = | producer = | editor = | camera = | runtime = | company = | distributor = | network = [[MBC 1 (Middle East and North Africa)|MBC 1]] | picture_format = | audio_format = | first_aired = 2016 | last_aired = 2017 | website = | production_website = http://www.mbc.net/ar/programs/al-sadma.html }}
'''The Shock''' or '''Alsadma''' ({{lang-ar|'''برنامج الصدمة'''}}), is a [[television program]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mbc.net/ar/programs/al-sadma.html|title=الصدمة - MBC مصر 2|publisher=MBC.net|date=7 July 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sayidaty.net/node/575386/%D8%A3%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%88%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%AA%D9%85%D8%B9/%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%AA%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%86-%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%86/%C2%AB%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AC-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9%C2%BB-%D8%A3%D8%AB%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9|title=«برنامج الصدمة» أثار في المشاهدين الصدمة &#124; مجلة سيدتي|language={{ar icon}}|publisher=Sayidaty.net|date=7 June 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hiamag.com/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%B1/593376-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AC-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9|title=برنامج الصدمة - مجلة هي|language={{ar icon}}|publisher=Hiamag.com|date=27 May 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hiamag.com/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%B1/%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8/593756-%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D9%84%D9%82%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AC-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9|title=شاهد الحلقة الأولى من برنامج "الصدمة" - مجلة هي|language={{ar icon}}|publisher=Hiamag.com|date=27 May 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hiamag.com/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%B1/593866-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%85%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%BA-%D9%88%D8%BA%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D9%85%D9%82%D9%86%D8%B9|title=الصدمة: أداء مبالغ وغير مقنع - مجلة هي|language={{ar icon}}|publisher=Hiamag.com|date=28 May 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref> of the category of hidden [[camera]], which was shown on [[MBC 1 (Middle East and North Africa)|MBC 1]] in [[Ramadan]] 2016, and it was a great success, which made the production company envision a second season, which was shown throughout the [[Ramadan]] of 2017. Starring [[Alaa Hussein (actress)|Alaa Huusein]] and Karim Kojak.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elcinema.com/work/2047101|title=الصدمة 2 - ﺑﺮﻧﺎﻣﺞ - 2017 - طاقم العمل، فيديو، الإعلان، صور، النقد الفني، مواعيد العرض|publisher=Elcinema.com|date=|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://shahid.mbc.net/ar/shows/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-param-.season-236340/show-141687|title=الصدمة - Shahid.net|publisher=Shahid.mbc.net|date=|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=الاسم *|url=http://www.lallafatima.ma/%D9%87%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D9%83%D8%B4%D9%81-%D8%AA%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8A%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%82-%D8%B9%D9%85|title=هشام الوالي يكشف تفاصيل مغادرة فريق عمل الصدمة المغرب &#124;|publisher=Lallafatima.ma|date=3 January 2018|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref>
Silvia Caos and Raúl Farell starred as protagonists.
== Cast == * [[Alaa Hussein (actress)|Alaa Huusein]] * Karim Kojak * Khaled Alsaqer * Turki Al Yousef * Tarek Sweid * Ahmed Landolsi * Nancy Khoury
==Morocco refused to portray the program== After the success of the first season, the team decided to add other countries to the list of countries in which the program is being filmed. The country was chosen from the [[Arab states of the Persian Gulf|Persian Gulf]], Jordan and Europe from Germany, then from North Africa, Morocco, but the latter replaced Tunisia until the last words. After the "Moroccan Ministry of Communication"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al-watan.com/news-details/id/82332|title=أسرار منع تصوير «الصدمة»|publisher=Al-watan.com|date=12 June 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=فاطمة عاشور (الرباط)|url=http://www.lahamag.com/article/93179-%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%B5-%D9%84%D9%87%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AC-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%85%D9%86%D9%88%D8%B9-%D8%AA%D8%B5%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D9%88%D9%85%D8%A7-%D9%87%D9%88-%D9%85%D9%88%D9%82%D9%81-mbc|title=خاص "لها"- برنامج الصدمة ممنوع تصويره بالمغرب وما هو موقف mbc &#124; Laha Magazine|publisher=Lahamag.com|date=6 June 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://masr140.com/%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B9%D8%AF-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AC-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-2-%D8%B1%D9%85%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%86-2017|title=موعد برنامج الصدمة 2 على قناة ام بي سي مصر "mbc" - توقيت اعادة برنامج الصدمة لكريم كوجاك "مقلب جديد"|publisher=Masr140.com|date=|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=1|url=https://www.alwatanvoice.com/arabic/news/2017/05/31/1055568.html|title=موعد برنامج الصدمة 2 في رمضان 2017 &#124; دنيا الوطن|publisher=Alwatanvoice.com|date=31 May 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alyaoum24.com/887327.html|title=“جهات أمنية” منعت تصوير برنامج “الصدمة 2 ” في المغرب – اليوم 24|publisher=Alyaoum24.com|date=1 June 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=1 دقائق قراءة|url=http://soltana.ma/285929.html|title=المغرب يرفض الترخيص لـ MBC بتصوير برنامج "الصدمة" وتونس ترحب به|publisher=Soltana.ma|date=10 April 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=الاسم|url=http://www.alittihad.info/%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B5%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8|title=Al Itihad|publisher=Alittihad.info|date=5 March 2017|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref><ref>http://www.almaghribtoday.net/196/041531-%D9%85%D8%AE%D8%B7%D8%B7-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B5%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D9%8A%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D8%AE%D8%B5%D8%A9-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8</ref> refused to grant the license to the team, citing that "the program discredits Morocco and that it affects the rights of women and children."
